TopicTitle: My KSP crashes all the time.

Articles.Content:
Please read http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/threads/92229-How-To-Get-Support-%28READ-FIRST%29 and post the output_log.txt file.

You might be running out of memory. The 32-bit version can only use ~3.1 GB of RAM, regardless of how much your system has.

Your options include (1) uninstalling some mods, (2) installing Active Texture Manager, (3) there is a trick forcing OpenGL mode? (I am not familiar with this option)
